-spec number_of_powerful_int(Start :: integer(), Finish :: integer(), Limit :: integer(), S :: unicode:unicode_binary()) -> integer().
number_of_powerful_int(Start, Finish, Limit, S) ->
    Suffix = binary_to_integer(S),
    GenerateNumbers = fun G(Num, Acc) when Num > Limit -> Acc;
                          G(Num, Acc) ->
                              NewNum = Num * trunc(math:pow(10, byte_size(S))) + Suffix,
                              if 
                                  NewNum >= Start, NewNum =< Finish -> G(Num + 1, [NewNum | Acc]);
                                  true -> G(Num + 1, Acc)
                              end
                      end,
    FilteredNumbers = lists:foldl(fun(X, Acc) ->
                                      Numbers = GenerateNumbers(X, []),
                                      Acc ++ Numbers
                                  end, [], [0|lists:seq(1, Limit)]),
    length(lists:usort(FilteredNumbers)).
